data.text:
SIKSUKR

Definately confirmed.I just watched Jimmy on the Today show and he was asked about the name.He said he got married at the lake so they named her after Winnipesaukee.

Irish mist

Congrats to them. Like many people they have an emotional connection to the lake. Still think the PTB are pushing Leno out too early for Fallon, but it is what it is:)

Aguamenti

Apparently he vacations at the lake. Wondered where?

I have heard they have a home on Sewell Road in Wolfeboro. He was at the 4th of July parade in Wolfeboro this year.

chasedawg

I have heard they have a home on Sewell Road in Wolfeboro. He was at the 4th of July parade in Wolfeboro this year.

Jimmy's wife Nancy parents have a home at point of Sewell Road. Jim dated Nancy several summers at the her parents home. Jimmy is also good friends with Drew Barrymore who stays at a home not far from Nancy's parents. If you come around the lighted marker at the very Sewell Road point there is a flag pole on a dock and that is where the folklore says Jimmy proposed to Nancy. Very nice story now that they named their daughter after their favorite lake.
